<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA514_04_IH_0002_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema514_04.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema514_04_ih_0002">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y" class="fraction_box_title">
          <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>16</span>
                <span>24</span>
              </div>
              을 기약분수로 나타내려고 합니다. <span class="empty_box nemo"></span>안에 알맞은 수를 써넣으세요.
            </div>
          </div>          
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <div class="question_box justify_center">
            <div class="text_bullet flex align_center gap_12" lang="y">
              24와 16의 최대공약수는
              <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="8"></math-field></div>
              <span class="ml-10">입니다.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">분모와 분자를 그들의 최대공약수로 나누면 기약분수로 나타낼 수 있으므로 분모와 분자의 최대공약수인 8로 분모와 분자를 각각 나눕니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <div class="question_box dir_col">
            <div class="text_bullet flex align_center gap_12" lang="y">
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>16</span>
                <span>24</span>
              </div>
              <span class="ml-10">을 기약분수로 나타내면</span>

              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>16</span>
                <span>24</span>
              </div>
              =
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <div class="flex align_center">
                  <span>16 ÷</span>
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="8"></math-field></div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex align_center">
                  <span>24 ÷</span>
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="8"></math-field></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              =
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field></div>
                <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field></div>
              </div>
              <span class="ml-10">입니다.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">분모와 분자를 그들의 최대공약수로 나누면 기약분수로 나타낼 수 있으므로 분모와 분자의 최대공약수인 8로 분모와 분자를 각각 나눕니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
